entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Sa w vle?" t="What do you want?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="M pa gen tan." t="Ain't got time." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Veye l!" t="Watch it!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Sa te fout …" t="What the…" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Tann yon ti moman… Ou pat wè frè m lan…? Sa fè kèk jou… En… Se byen sa." t="Just a second… Didn't you see my brother…? A few days… Yeah… Definitely." b="" a=""/>

<kiroshi l="creo" o="Mwen pè … yo pa kraze msye… Se sa menm… Mwen vle espere sa … Fòk mwen kwè sa. Fòk manman m tou kwè sa." t="I'm scared… that they got him… Exactly… I hope not… I got to. Mom too." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Mèsi. Nap kenbe kontak." t="Thanks. Keep in touch." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Gèt manman vil sa a!" t="Fuck this city!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Fè pa m. Bonm lavi!" t="Make mine. Give me life." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Mwen pa fè w anyen!" t="I haven't done anything to you!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Mwen pa vle gen pwoblèm. Ou menm tou ou pa vle sa." t="I don't want trouble. Neither do you." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Mwen wè wap siv mwen." t="I can see that you're following me." b="" a=""/>
